  "doc_id": "44925",
  "text": "The algorithm proposed to determine an optimal distribution of buffers to balance a DFG can be compared to the Simplex Algorithm [CITATION_1] , which is normally applied for linear programming. Our algorithm is applied to DFGs and the solution is reached in polynomial time for this particular problem. The algorithm consists of two main steps. First, we assign buffers to the DFG to balance the graph. In the second step, we minimize the number of buffers while maintaining the balanced structure of the DFG.",
